data.description:
Escape to tranquility just outside Whitney city limits and minutes from the lake. This charming 3-bed, 2-bath brick home sets on nearly 4 acres of opportunity. Conveniently located a mere 3.5 miles from the nearest boat ramp at Parsons Marina, this property is a haven for vacationers and investors alike.
Inside, discover modern updates including a refreshed kitchen and recent roof & HVAC replacements. With ample acreage ripe for expansion, envision additional income-generating structures to capitalize on the thriving rental market. Plus, a spacious detached garage and fenced perimeter offer security and versatility.
Whether seeking a peaceful retreat or a savvy investment, this property offers the best of both worlds. Don't miss out – seize this prime opportunity today!
